title: 245.62 COMMUNITY MENTAL HEALTH CENTER.
text:
Any city, county, town, combination thereof, or private nonprofit corporation may establish a community mental health center.
A community mental health center is a private nonprofit corporation or public agency approved under the standards of section 256B.0625, subdivision 5.
MS 2020 [Repealed, 2021 c 30 art 17 s 113]
